  <div id="text-content_3a32ed95-14a2-4a43-9f33-f204623e5322" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Save</strong> button. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="close_for_comments" data-step-uuid="E177F898-FFBD-497D-B312-FBF476FA98C7">
    <h2 id="close_for_comments" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Close in Announcements Page</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/496/403/original/4aaece5c-2aa7-4261-aecd-478299a3db67.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/496/403/medium/4aaece5c-2aa7-4261-aecd-478299a3db67.png" srcset="" alt="Close in Announcements Page" height="487" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_3F0EBB10-1E1D-0135-C021-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To close an announcement for comments from the index page, locate the announcement. Click the <strong>Options</strong> icon [1] and click the <strong>Disallow Comments</strong> link [2]. </p>
<p>To close more than one announcement for comments from the index page, click the checkbox next to each announcement [3] and click the <strong>Lock Reply</strong> button [4].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="open_to_comments" data-step-uuid="4d6d07e5-6498-4f17-908f-c20cb8244300">
    <h3 id="open_to_comments" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open for Comments</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/496/406/original/ddd9ff5a-3d7c-4ea4-a38a-e757e64f4c62.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/496/406/medium/ddd9ff5a-3d7c-4ea4-a38a-e757e64f4c62.png" srcset="" alt="Open for Comments" height="388" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_3F109640-1E1D-0135-C025-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To open an announcement for comments, locate the announcement and click the <strong>Options</strong> icon [1], then click the <strong>Allow Comments </strong>link [2]. </p>
<p>To open more than one announcement for comments from the index page, click the checkbox next to each announcement [3] and click the <strong>Lock Reply</strong> button [4].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="close-from-individual-announcement" data-step-uuid="16a744d6-5e51-4664-8a65-56f22edf3b45">
    <h2 id="close-from-individual-announcement" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Close Individual Open Announcement</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/487/908/original/95343dee-e3b6-40f0-b38b-bcac891311b0.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
