      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_141614bd-7ee5-41c0-88a6-d57e08a92bbe" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To close comments in an open announcement, click the name of the announcement.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="close-for-comments" data-step-uuid="24c21a84-b870-41b0-9965-3fe08da484c3">
